QuestData.Title: The Pride of Lok-rath
QuestData.Description: You think the Warsong are so easily defeated?$B$B<There's a rasping sound, like rope on metal.>$B$BI'm already tired of you Alliance, and you've just invaded my homeland.$B$B<The sound becomes more pronounced as Uruk Foecleaver looks you straight in the eye.>$B$BThere will be no surrender. The Warsong bow to no one!
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Kill the Warsong Commander of Lok-rath.
QuestData.RewardText: Unfortunate, but I'm glad you made it out of that trap alive.
